high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table on your right.
Grab some lettuce from the table.
Walk to the fridge behind you to your left.
Put the lettuce in the fridge, then take it out.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your left.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill some lettuce and put it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the white table then take a step to your right to stand in front of the lettuce.
Pick up the lettuce that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the fridge then turn left to face it when you get there.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the sink then turn right to face it.
Put the lettuce in the sink to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold head of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the right side of the white table.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Cool the lettuce off in the fridge then take it out.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold lettuce in the sink.
